[[Far Boorama]] (sidoo kale loo yaqaano Far Gadabuursi) waxaa alifey [[Sheekh Cabdiraxmaan Sheekh Nuur]] oo macalin ka ahaa magaalada [[Boorama]].<ref>{{cite book|author=David D. Laitin|title=Politics, Language, and Thought: The Somali Experience|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=LR8A4tEYZUAC&pg=PA98|accessdate=2 July 2012|date=1 May 1977|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=978-0-226-46791-7|pages=98‚Äì}}</ref> 
Nidaamka qorida Farta Boorama waa mid aad uga duwan Farta Cusmaaniya. Fartani waxay leedahay shaqalo gaaban iyo kuwo dhaadheer, hakadyo iyo hingaad intaba ka dhex muuqata qoraalka.<ref>I.M. Lewis (1958), [http://www.scribd.com/doc/15957443/The-Gadabursi-Somali-Script The Gadabuursi Somali Script], ''Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies'', University of London, Vol. 21, pp. 134‚Äì156.</ref> 

Inkastoo aanay soo shaacbixin isla markiiba, maanta waxaa la helayaa qoraalo badan iskugu jira diini, gabayo, cilmi iyo taariikh oo Sheekh Cabdiraxmaan iyo xertiisu ku qoreen Farta Boorama.<ref> the Borama script was principally used by Nuur and his circle of associates in his native city of [[Boorama|Borama]].</ref>

==Farta Kaddare==
{{main|Far Kaddare}}
[[Farta Kaddare]] waxaa alifey [[Xuseen Sheekh Axmed Kaddare]] sanadkii 1952dii.<ref>{{cite book|last=Laitin|first=David D.|title=Politics, Language, and Thought: The Somali Experience|year=1977|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=0226467910|page=87|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=LR8A4tEYZUAC}}</ref> 
Nidaamka qoraalka fartani waxay aad ugu qaab dhowdahay farta Cusmaaniya, laakiin waxay kaga duwan tahay nidaamka shaqaleynta iyo adkeynta ereyada.<ref>[http://www.skyknowledge.com/kaddare.htm Simon Ager, Kaddare transcription]</ref>

